name: full circle
description:
ever since i was young 'un - i wanted to set a couch alight and photograph it.

when i was in my early 20's, i owned this dusky pink sofa set. but when i left that town, i had to leave them behind.

when i returned to that city a few years later, i stumbled across the same couch set in an opshop - complete with my coffee stain and cat scratches.

all was groovy until my flatmate sat on it and crushed it, so i fulfilled my childhood dreams, and took it down to the bay to set it alight.

a full circle moment. anything you let go will come back if it is meant to be.
